elements.expression:
filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT \"@timestamp\", (transaction.duration.us / 1000) as latency FROM \"apm-*\" WHERE transaction.name = 'component1Flow' AND transaction.duration.us < 100000 ORDER BY \"@timestamp\" DESC LIMIT 300"
| pointseries y="mean(latency)" x="@timestamp"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle lines=1 fill=1} xaxis=false yaxis={axisConfig position="left"}
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown "#### Average request latency (ms, last 300 requests)"
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT count(*) FROM \"apm-*\" WHERE transaction.name = 'component1Flow'"
| math "COUNT_1_"
| metric "Transactions processed" 
  metricFont={font size=48 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center" lHeight=48} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

| pointseries x="span.name" y="mean(duration)" color="span.name"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle bars=0.75} legend=false
| render
